name: Untitled Square Game
description: Untitled Square game is an simple game made in godot in the time period of 24 hours. It was not for any kind of game jam but the developer took this as an challenge and made the game under 24 hours! It may have some bugs and the game may look bad but you can't question it because it was made in 24 hours lol. Watch this video for more info about how the game was made and also don't forget to subscribe to the developer's channel!!
